commit.message: Added a watch app. It has similar functionality to the iOS app, but does not track life totals.
Made it easier to read some of the text.
Prevent the setting for life total to be changed to a non-Int value.
Changed the decrease and uptick Life tab to change text color to red when the value is negative.
Fixes

Forgot to commit final changes before 11. Oops.

Added a cog and settings to the name.
I added even more. Settings work.
Lots of things chaned.
Added a Launch page with the correct image and app name.
Added a background and support for rolling two d6.

* Added an image of a D20
* Added functionality that allows user to roll a D20.

* Created tabs
* Created a random file
* Created a CoinView and DiceView controller for their respective tabs
* D6 button is now a D6
* Coin flip button now changes color to show that the coin has been flipped.
* Pictures for Heads or Tails
* and more!

iOS: Created a slider. Slider has min of 1, max of 10. When the slider is moved the value (an int instead of a float) is put onto the label.
Additionally, we are now using Horizontal and Vertical alignment to make it fit for all kinds of iOS devices.
Watch: Set up the watch.
iOS: Created 2 buttons. One label. Leftmost button changes text from Hello World to Goodbye world. Rightmost button changes text to a random number.
Initial Commit
